<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.1.8">
<l>vāḷā vākilum kāṇakil lārpiṟar makkaḷai maiyaṉmai ceytu</l>
<l>tōḷā liṭṭava rōṭu tiḷaittunī collap paṭātaṉa ceytāy</l>
<l>kēḷā rayar kulattava rippaḻi keṭṭēṉvāḻ villai nantaṟ</l>
<l>kāḷā yuṉṉai yaṟintukoṇ ṭēṉuṉakkañcuva ṉammam taravē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if [your wickedness] comes to nought,</l>
<l rend="indent">having infatuated the ladies [of the village],</l>
<l rend="indent">the others will not see [it this way].</l>
<l>Having embraced them, grasping [their] shoulders,</l>
<l rend="indent">you have done unspeakable things.</l>
<l>Those of the herder clan will not tolerate these crimes!</l>
<l rend="indent">I am ruined! I have no life!</l>
<l>Ruler of Nanda! I have come to know you,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] I am afraid to give you [my] breast milk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
